title: Greece Chamber of Commerce to offer travel information
text: Greece Chamber of Commerce to offer travel information Comment   2:47 PM Updated at 2:47 PM   2:47 PM Greece, N.Y. The Greece Chamber of Commerce, 2402 W. Ridge Road, will hold free travel information sessions Sept. 2 and 16 and Oct. 7. Discovering Poland: 6 p.m. Sept. 2. Travel dates will be Sept 22.-Oct. 3. Great Trains and Grand Canyons: 5:30 p.m. Sept. 16. Travel dates will be May 15-20. Nova Scotia and the Canadian Maritimes: 6:45 p.m. Sept. 16. Travel dates will be July 13-21. Costa del Sol and the Portuguese RIviera: 6 p.m. Oct. 7. Travel dates will be Nov. 10-22. For more information, call 585-227-7272 or visit greecechamber.org/travel . Greece Post
